    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Boxy tables or case pieces on tall legs, used for serving food. Characterized by having no lower shelf, and occasionally drawers. Originally used outdoors for serving hunting parties.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
